Task 6 - Fraud Detection

Objective:
To detect fraudulent credit card transactions using machine learning.

 Dataset:
[Credit Card Fraud Detection â€“ Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud)

